#. <section class="sutta" id="sn48.49"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.49:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.49:0.2"
msgid "5. Jarāvagga"
msgstr "5. Old Age"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 49. Piṇḍolabhāradvājasutta → piṇḍolasuttaṃ (bj) | piṇḍolo (pts1)
msgctxt "sn48.49:0.3"
msgid "49. Piṇḍolabhāradvājasutta"
msgstr "49. About Piṇḍola Bhāradvāja"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.49:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "sn48.49:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosambiyaṃ viharati ghositārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Kosambi, in Ghosita’s Monastery."

msgctxt "sn48.49:1.3"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmatā piṇḍolabhāradvājena aññā byākatā hoti:"
msgstr ""
"Now at that time Venerable Piṇḍola Bhāradvāja had declared enlightenment:"

msgctxt "sn48.49:1.4"
msgid ""
"“khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyāti "
"pajānāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“I understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, "
"what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of "
"existence.’”"

msgctxt "sn48.49:1.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho sambahulā bhikkhū yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho te "
"bhikkhū bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr ""
"Then several mendicants went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, "
"and told him what had happened. Then they said:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.49:2.1"
msgid "“Āyasmatā, bhante, piṇḍolabhāradvājena aññā byākatā:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn48.49:2.2"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānāmīti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn48.49:2.3"
msgid ""
"Kiṃ nu kho, bhante, atthavasaṃ sampassamānena āyasmatā piṇḍolabhāradvājena "
"aññā byākatā:"
msgstr "“What reason does Piṇḍola Bhāradvāja see for doing this?”"

msgctxt "sn48.49:2.4"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānāmī”ti?"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.225"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.49:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Tiṇṇannaṃ kho, bhikkhave, indriyānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā "
"piṇḍolabhāradvājena bhikkhunā aññā byākatā:"
msgstr ""
"“It’s because Piṇḍola Bhāradvāja has developed and cultivated three "
"faculties that he declares enlightenment:"

msgctxt "sn48.49:3.2"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānāmīti."
msgstr ""
"‘I understand: “Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, "
"what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of "
"existence.”’"

msgctxt "sn48.49:3.3"
msgid "Katamesaṃ tiṇṇannaṃ?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "sn48.49:3.4"
msgid "Satindriyassa, samādhindriyassa, paññindriyassa—"
msgstr "The faculties of mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom."

msgctxt "sn48.49:3.5"
msgid ""
"imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tiṇṇannaṃ indriyānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā "
"piṇḍolabhāradvājena bhikkhunā aññā byākatā:"
msgstr ""
"It’s because Piṇḍola Bhāradvāja has developed and cultivated these three "
"faculties that he declares enlightenment."

msgctxt "sn48.49:3.6"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānāmīti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn48.49:3.7"
msgid "Imāni ca, bhikkhave, tīṇindriyāni kimantāni?"
msgstr "What’s the culmination of these three faculties?"

msgctxt "sn48.49:3.8"
msgid "Khayantāni."
msgstr "They culminate in ending."

msgctxt "sn48.49:3.9"
msgid "Kissa khayantāni?"
msgstr "In the ending of what?"

msgctxt "sn48.49:3.10"
msgid "Jātijarāmaraṇassa."
msgstr "Of rebirth, old age, and death."

msgctxt "sn48.49:3.11"
msgid ""
"‘Jātijarāmaraṇaṃ khayan’ti kho, bhikkhave, sampassamānena "
"piṇḍolabhāradvājena bhikkhunā aññā byākatā:"
msgstr ""
"It’s because he sees that they culminate in the ending of rebirth, old age, "
"and death that Piṇḍola Bhāradvāja declares enlightenment:"

msgctxt "sn48.49:3.12"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I understand: “Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, "
"what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of "
"existence.”’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.49:3.13"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
